      {# ── Author cards ── #}
      <section class="sg-section" id="author-cards">
        <h2>Author cards</h2>
        <p class="lead">Used on the Contributors page. Centered column layout: avatar on top, body below. The avatar uses a stacked pattern, initials always rendered, photo absolutely positioned on top with <code>onerror</code> fallback.</p>

        <div class="sg-demo">
          <div style="max-width: 280px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <article class="author-card">
              <div class="author-card__avatar">
                <div class="author-card__initials" aria-hidden="true">JA</div>
              </div>
              <div class="author-card__body">
                <p class="author-card__role">Founding Editor</p>
                <h2 class="author-card__name"><a href="/author/jon-ajinga/">Jon Ajinga</a></h2>
                <p class="author-card__bio">Covering regulation, institutional power, and the life of ideas.</p>
                <div class="author-card__stats">
                  <span class="author-card__stat"><strong>15</strong> articles</span>
                  <span class="author-card__stat"><strong>7.8k</strong> words</span>
                  <span class="author-card__stat"><strong>~47m</strong> reading</span>
                </div>
                <div class="author-card__footer">
                  <a class="author-card__link" href="/author/jon-ajinga/">View articles &rarr;</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="sg-subsection">
          <h4>Avatar stacking pattern</h4>
          <pre class="sg-code">&lt;div class="author-card__avatar"&gt;
  &lt;div class="author-card__initials" aria-hidden="true"&gt;JA&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;img src="photo.jpg" class="author-card__photo"
       onerror="this.style.opacity=0"&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</pre>
          <p>Initials always render. Photo is <code>position: absolute</code> on top. <code>onerror</code> hides the photo if it fails to load, revealing initials underneath.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      {# ── Forms ── #}
      <section class="sg-section" id="forms">
        <h2>Forms</h2>
        <p class="lead">All inputs are minimum 44px tall, set in the UI typeface, and show a distinct focus ring. Forms are handled by embedded third-party providers (Web3Forms, Fillout, Zite), never custom backends.</p>

        <div class="sg-demo">
          <form class="form" onsubmit="event.preventDefault();">
            <div class="form__row">
              <label class="form__label form__label--required" for="sg-name">Name</label>
              <input class="form__input" id="sg-name" type="text" placeholder="Your name" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form__row">
              <label class="form__label" for="sg-email">Email</label>
              <input class="form__input" id="sg-email" type="email" placeholder="you@example.com">
              <p class="form__hint">We'll never share this.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="form__row">
              <label class="form__label" for="sg-select">Section</label>
              <select class="form__select" id="sg-select">
                <option>Pick one</option>
                <option>News</option>
                <option>Opinion</option>
                <option>Analysis</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form__row">
              <label class="form__label" for="sg-textarea">Message</label>
              <textarea class="form__textarea" id="sg-textarea" placeholder="Say something…"></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="form__actions">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn--accent">Submit</button>
              <button type="button" class="btn">Cancel</button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </section>

      {# ── Tables ── #}
      <section class="sg-section" id="tables">
        <h2>Tables</h2>
        <p class="lead">Data tables wrap in <code>.table-wrap</code> for horizontal scroll on narrow viewports. Use <code>scope="col"</code> on header cells and <code>scope="row"</code> on row headers.</p>

        <div class="sg-demo" style="padding: 0;">
          <div class="table-wrap">
            <table class="compare-table">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="col">Criterion</th>
                  <th scope="col">{{ site.title }}<small>independent</small></th>
                  <th scope="col">Ad-funded outlet<small>commercial</small></th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><th scope="row">Revenue model</th><td>Reader-funded</td><td>Advertisers</td></tr>
                <tr><th scope="row">Editorial control</th><td>Full</td><td>Partial</td></tr>
                <tr><th scope="row">Paywall</th><td>None</td><td>Often</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
        <pre class="sg-code">&lt;div class="table-wrap"&gt;
  &lt;table class="compare-table"&gt;…&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</pre>
      </section>

      {# ── Icons ── #}
      <section class="sg-section" id="icons">
        <h2>Icons</h2>
        <p class="lead">Icons are inline SVG, 24×24 viewBox, <code>stroke-width: 2</code>, <code>fill: none</code>, <code>currentColor</code>, they inherit text color automatically in light and dark modes.</p>

        <div class="sg-demo">
          <div class="sg-icon-grid">
            <div class="sg-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="24" height="24"><path d="M3 6h18M3 12h18M3 18h18"/></svg><span class="sg-icon__name">menu</span></div>
            <div class="sg-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="24" height="24"><path d="M6 6l12 12M18 6l-12 12"/></svg><span class="sg-icon__name">close</span></div>
            <div class="sg-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="24" height="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg><span class="sg-icon__name">chevron</span></div>
            <div class="sg-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" width="24" height="24"><path d="M12 19V5M6 11l6-6 6 6"/></svg><span class="sg-icon__name">arrow-up</span></div>
            <div class="sg-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="24" height="24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/><path d="M12 3v2M12 19v2M3 12h2M19 12h2"/></svg><span class="sg-icon__name">sun</span></div>
